import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0):
    v0 = jnp.cos(x0)
    v1 = jnp.maximum(x0, v0)
    v2 = jnp.minimum(v0, x0)
    v3 = jnp.maximum(v2, v2)
    v4 = jnp.abs(v1)
    v5 = jnp.subtract(v2, v4)
    v6 = jnp.tanh(v0)
    v7 = jnp.subtract(v5, v4)
    v8 = jnp.sin(v4)
    v9 = jnp.multiply(v3, v2)
    return v9
